						<a:Comment>Technical cash flow of facs</a:Comment>
						<a:TotalSavingCurrency/>
						<a:Annotation>That table serves to support of batch edition presenting fac cash flow. 

It updates monthly.

Totals are stocked in subsidiary currency and convert to statistic rate, that is the rate of 31/12 of previous year of subscription year.

Their volume increase of 6000lines by month. 

Cash flow = paid premium - charges - paid disaster - cash deposit - paid interest</a:Annotation>
