					<o:Table Id="o226">
						<a:ObjectID>2BBA78D2-5C86-4E0C-B01B-D0167B39B21E</a:ObjectID>
						<a:Name>Statistic parameters table</a:Name>
						<a:Code>TPARAM</a:Code>
						<a:CreationDate>860680380</a:CreationDate>
						<a:Creator>OME08</a:Creator>
						<a:ModificationDate>860680380</a:ModificationDate>
						<a:Modifier>OME08</a:Modifier>
						<a:Comment>Parameters table of statistic application</a:Comment>
						<a:TotalSavingCurrency/>
						<a:Description>Table of parameters of counting application.

Parameters of type amount are expressed in subsidiary currency.
Parameters of type duration in days.
In others case : 1 =&gt; option available, 0 =&gt; option not available.</a:Description>
						<a:Annotation>Managment rules of general purpose tables : 

PCS_CF is the login of treatment set who have specific parameters expected. 

PARAMi_N (i=1 to 20)are 20 parameters possible in a treatment. 
To know the parameters list of a treatment, check the table BREF..TBANALL with col_ls = 'PARAM_CF'. colval_ls is equals to : PCS_CF * 100 + i (n of parameters)</a:Annotation>
						<c:Columns>
