						<a:ModificationDate>860680380</a:ModificationDate>
						<a:Modifier>OME08</a:Modifier>
						<a:Comment>Report activity of facs</a:Comment>
						<a:TotalSavingCurrency/>
						<a:Annotation>That table serves to support of batch edition presenting fac activity report. 

It updates monthly.

It contains datas of 24 later months. Their volume is estimated to 6000linesfor Europe site. 
It can update the table TFACACTA. Totals are stocked in subsidiary currency and convert to statistic rate, that is the rate of 31/12 of previous year of subscription year.</a:Annotation>
