					<o:Table Id="o230">
						<a:ObjectID>A1A0DC99-58FE-4201-8CC1-5CC7BB958828</a:ObjectID>
						<a:Name>Fac activity synthesis A</a:Name>
						<a:Code>TFACACTA</a:Code>
						<a:CreationDate>860680380</a:CreationDate>
						<a:Creator>OME08</a:Creator>
						<a:ModificationDate>860680380</a:ModificationDate>
						<a:Modifier>OME08</a:Modifier>
						<a:Comment>Report activity of inter sites fac, 1st denormalization</a:Comment>
						<a:TotalSavingCurrency/>
						<a:Annotation>That table serves to support of batch edition presenting fac activity report. 

It is erased and filled in by TFACACT, in monthly batch which filled in TFACACT

It contains datas of all sites. It represent a first destandardization of TFACACT : we added all datas between the beginning year to treatment month.  Their volume is estimated to 105000lines
Totals are stocked in subsidiary currency and convert to statistic rate, that is the rate of 31/12 of previous year of subscription year. We define cluster index &lt;Year,Month,Subsidiary&gt;.</a:Annotation>
						<c:Columns>
							<o:Column Id="o757">
								<a:ObjectID>7A8F2B8D-E884-4B63-8550-CAE0B5B8C365</a:ObjectID>
								<a:Name>Fac activity synthesis number</a:Name>
								<a:Code>FACACT_NT</a:Code>
								<a:CreationDate>860680380</a:CreationDate>
								<a:Creator>OME08</a:Creator>
								<a:ModificationDate>860680380</a:ModificationDate>
								<a:Modifier>OME08</a:Modifier>
								<a:Comment>Fac activity synthesis number</a:Comment>
								<a:DataType>numeric(10)</a:DataType>
								<a:Length>10</a:Length>
								<a:Identity>1</a:Identity>
								<a:Mandatory>1</a:Mandatory>
