						<a:TotalSavingCurrency/>
						<a:Annotation>That table serves to support of windows presenting fac accumulation statistic. It is erased and filled in by TFACSTA, in monthly batch which filled in TFACSTA. It contains treatment month datas of all sites.  Their volume is estimated to 80000lines. Totals are stocked in subsidiary currency and convert to statistic rate, that is the rate of 31/12 of previous year of subscription year.</a:Annotation>
