						<a:Code>TFACSTA</a:Code>
						<a:CreationDate>860680380</a:CreationDate>
						<a:Creator>OME08</a:Creator>
						<a:ModificationDate>860680380</a:ModificationDate>
						<a:Modifier>OME08</a:Modifier>
						<a:Comment>Statistics accumulated of fac</a:Comment>
						<a:TotalSavingCurrency/>
						<a:Annotation>That table serve to support of windows presenting fac accumulation statistic

It is filled in monthly and erased before every filling.

It contains datas linked to treatment month.

Their volume is estimated to 40000 lines for Europe site. 

It permits to fill in the table TFACSTAA.

Totals are stocked in subsidiary currency and convert to statistic rate, that is the rate of 31/12 of previous year of subscription year.</a:Annotation>
