						<a:Comment></a:Comment>
						<a:TotalSavingCurrency/>
						<a:Description>Table composed by :   
  - account informations acceptation; retrocession selected according to tables : TTECLEDA_98, TTECLEDR_98 for datas on debtor society

- settlement informations acceptation; retrocession according to table TCURTRS for datas on old balance.

Posts are grouped by code PCR  (reinsurance counting plan).
Amounts are converted in FF on the last known price.
That table is created for information center ( used by Bo ).


JMB 11-03-2008 - spot 15036 :
Add column LOCAL_CF, permit to stock a actual old balance (0, default value), or a "local" old balance, for the needs ex-revios, ex-converium and soon SCOR
</a:Description>
