								<a:Comment>tranche balance agée</a:Comment>
								<a:DataType>tinyint</a:DataType>
								<a:Mandatory>1</a:Mandatory>
								<a:Description>Indicate the duration between transaction date and end date. 

0 - no calculation ( credit/debit society )

 1 to 6  only concern age balance
1 - superior to 12 month
2 - superior to 6 month and inferior or equals to 12 month
3 - superior to 3 month and inferior or equals to 6 month 
4 - superior to 2 month and inferior or equals to 3 month  
5 - superior to 1 month and inferior or equals to 2 month
6 - inferior or equals to 30 days.</a:Description>
